== Abrabɔ Mfitiaseɛ ==
Wɔ woo Nadia Buari ɛwɔ [[Sekondi-Takoradi]], [[Ghana]]. Ne papa y3 Lɛbanisnii, ɛna ne maame nso yɛ Ghananii. Ɔkɔɔ sukuu wɔ [[Mfantsiman Girls' Secondary School|Mfanteman Mmaa Sekondary Sukuu]]<ref>https://www.peacefmonline.com/pages/showbiz/news/201207/123699.php</ref>. Ɔwieɛ no, Nadia kɔ sua sinitwa ho adwuma ɛwɔ sukuupɔn a wɔfrɛ no [[Legon Suapon|University of Ghana]].<ref>https://yen.com.gh/109577-ghanaian-actress-nadia-buari-biography.html</ref> Ɔwɔ sukuu suapɔn nyinaa ara no na ɔbɔ ne ho mmɔden yie ɛwɔ sinitwa ne asa akuo a na ɔka ho mu no.

